156	// bound, a runtime AddPath fans a per-(peer,path) prober out to BOTH peers, each keyed on its
157	// OWN psk, and a RemovePath tears each peer's per-(peer,path) prober down. It exercises the
158	// runtime add/remove flow while >=2 peers are bound (the runtime path add/remove flow must work
